clean_prompt:
A binary search returns -1 for values that exist in the array. Debug this implementation:
def binary_search(arr, target):
    lo, hi = 0, len(arr)
    while lo < hi:
        mid = (lo + hi) // 2
        if arr[mid] < target:
            lo = mid + 1
        elif arr[mid] > target:
            hi = mid
        else:
            return mid
    return -1
